Pixas is an Open Source ActionScript engine, which enables programmers to build isometric pixel Flash Applications with pure ActionScript3. With Pixas you can easily add isometric pixel elements like brick, cube, pyramid, map layer to your applications.

Showcase - Pixas Editor: http://risonhuang.wordpress.com/pixas-editor/

Showcase - Uncle Big's Adventure: http://pixas.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/showcase/unclebig/index.html

Follow me on twitter: https://twitter.com/pixas_engine


Check out more about examples, tutorials and documents here: http://risonhuang.wordpress.com/pixas/

